would        terminacion /ria / verbos  *** pasado de will ** condicionales 2 y 3
would have   habria / hubiese  *** algo que habria / hubiese sucedido
  (woulda)
  
El haria lo mismo
- He would do the same.     He'd do the same
- He wouldn't do the same
- Would he do the same?  Wouldn't he do the same?


El habria/hubiera hecho lo mismo
- he would have done the same
- he wouldn't have done the same  (he wouldna the same --> se podria oir asi)
- would he have done the same?
  wouldn´t he have done the same?
  
  mayra estaria durmiendo en casa por  este clima frio
  mayra would be slepping in her house because of this cold wheater
  
  si ellos me ubieran preguntado, les habria dicho la verdad.
  if they had asked me, i would have told them the true
  
  
  me habria/hubiese desmayado si..
  i would have fainted if i had seen the gost
     (wouldda) 
  
