  must  vrs must have
deber obligacion - asumir algo
suj + must + v.base + complent     suj + must + have + vpp + complemento

alberto debe traer la comida
 - alberto must bring the food
 - alberto must not bring the food
 - must alberto bring the food
 
 alberto debe haber traido la comida
  - alberto must have brought the food
  - alberto must not have brougt the food
  - must have alberto brougt the food


1) no encuentro mis llaves. Debi dejarlas/haberlas dejado en la oficina
   i don't find my keys. I must have left them in the office

2) Debemos mostrar el pasaporte en la recepcion
we must shown the passport in the reception

3) Debieron mostrar/haber mostrado su pasaporte ayer
you must have shown your passport yesterday.

4) Debio anderson estudiar antes de su examen?
must have anderson studied before his exam?


