++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
should --> deberias (para dar consejo)
should have  --> deberia haber  debi haber

deberian haber mostrado el passaporte
you should have shown the passport.

1) deberiamos esperar el bus        debimos haber esperado el bus
  we should wait the bus	    we should have waited the bus
  
2) deberias contarnos               tu debiste habernos contado
 you should tell us                 you should have told us
 
 3) el deberia comprar el regalo     el debio haber comprado el regalo
 he should buy the present           he should have bought the present
 
 4) No deberiamos invitarlos          no debimos haberlos invitado
 we shouldn't have invited them       we shouldn't have invited theem
 
 5) deberia ella conducir el carro     debio ella haber manejado el carro
 Should she drive the car?             should have she driven the car?
 
 6) yo deberia perdonarte              deberia haberte perdonardo
 i should forgive you                  i should have forgiven you.
 
 
  
  
  
  



